sentences: Yukiji Asaoka (朝丘 雪路, Asaoka Yukiji, July 23, 1935 – April 27, 2018) was a Japanese singer and an actress from Chūō, Tokyo.
Asaoka was in the Takarazuka Revue from 1952 to 1955.
She was also a voice actor in the 1999 anime film My Neighbors the Yamadas directed by Isao Takahata.
